    <!-- WELCOME CONTENT -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
        <div class="container pt-5 pb-5">
            <h1 class="section-title">About Us</h1>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="about-content">
                        <p>
                            We simplify real estate selling, and renting. Join Ethio Homes for a new era of convenient
                            and transparent property management.
                        </p>
                        <img class="w-100 p-3" src="/images/about.jpg" alt="About Us">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="about-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
                                <h4>Comfortable</h4>
                                <p>Ethio Homes provides a comfortable real estate experience with its intuitive
                                    interface, extensive property listings, and secure online tools. Easily browse,
                                    negotiate, and finalize transactions all in one place, ensuring a stress-free
                                    process for buyers, sellers, and tenants.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <i class="fas fa-bullhorn"></i>
                                <h4>Efficiency</h4>
                                <p>Ethio Homes enhances efficiency in real estate transactions with its streamlined
                                    processes. From listing properties to finalizing agreements, our platform reduces
                                    time and effort, making the buying, selling, and renting experience faster and more
                                    straightforward for all users.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i>
                                <h4>Distribution</h4>
                                <p>Ethio Homes connects buyers, sellers, and renters from different locations, providing
                                    extensive reach and visibility for all properties. This comprehensive network
                                    facilitates efficient and effective real estate transactions nationwide.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <i class="fas fa-id-card-alt"></i>
                                <h4>Transparency</h4>
                                <p>Prioritizes transparency in all interactions. Detailed property descriptions, clear
                                    pricing information, and secure online agreements ensure that buyers, sellers, and
                                    tenants have all the information they need to make informed decisions confidently.
                                </p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

